	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hac hora, postquam tuas accepi, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingere</persName> compater in domino charissime, quaestorem <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerum</persName> propter causam D. <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Halleri</persName>, compatris nostri, tandem absolvendam accessi illique, quae ad me scripseris, exposui.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">Respondit ad hunc modum:</foreign> synes bedunckens achte er, das in diser sachen inn eynem radt allhie nichts für zuͦ nemen sye, er khünde dann selb darby im radt seyn; er khünde aber noch nit.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Darumb wüsse er hierin nichts zu handlen, byß er uff die fuͤß khome, hoff aber bald; dann wann er schon mitt dem herren <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Haller</persName> rede, was sin will und meinung sye, so sye es doch nur halb gmacht, diewil er noch nit personlich im radt darvon handlen khünde.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wann aber ir ein weg hetten, der euch baß gefiel, so mögen irs im schriben mitt einem bsonderen leufer; er welle demselben seynen lon geben etc.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec fere summa eorum est, quae mihi vir ille respondit.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Addidit se nondum oblitum esse eorum, quae ad se scripseris.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod me concernit, non possum satis mirari istam tarditatem et oscitantiam in causa ecclesię Christi; anxie vereor, ne quod nostris ecclesiis iudicio domini omnium iustissimo accidit, accidat etiam vestris.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Caeterum domus mea post obdormitionem <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20454">Iudith</persName>, filię meae, qua de iam antea scripsi, adhuc tranquilla est.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <persName type="auto_name">Eusebio</persName>, quem misi, non est opus ut tantopere gratias agas.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam possem humanitati tuae ac tuorum respondere, quam ostendistis in exules.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De rebus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Anglicis</placeName> scribuntur admodum tristia.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si quid certi acceperis, oro, communices.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Optime vale, virorum colendissime.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutem tuis omnibus et fratribus et dominis, domino <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicano</persName>, venerandissimo seni, D. <persName ref="p8171" cert="high">Bibliandro</persName>, D. <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gualthero</persName> et toti vestro <foreign xml:lang="el">[griechisch]</foreign>, etiam Gervasio nostro, cui cupiam obnixe tandem aliqua ratione esse consultum.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant vos mei omnes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName> 2. decembris 1549.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutem etiam D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4466">Butlero</persName> et quaestori <persName type="citizen_name">Neuburgico</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8417" cert="high">W[olfgangus] Musc[ulus]</persName>, compater tuus in domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo theologo M. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, compatri in domino charissimo.</s>
				</p>
